{"title":"Cardiomiopatias-2024-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Cardiología/Cardiomiopatias-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Cardiomiopatias","guid":"YcJJFBnN18lG8dLUNL9Ztg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Resumen","guid":"IgvFgdR_qzI4xpXcpiFeUw","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Definición: Enfermedades del tejido muscular cardíaco → afectan estructura/función.","guid":"tUi3-17vQ3_8QU9Pe8bVUA","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"• Tipos\\Nprincipales:","guid":"sc-o8D67FLygfMbpr_UcYA","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"• Cardiomiopatía dilatada\\N(DCM):","guid":"wm2VtnTr_OfZkDVNoEDnPQ","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"• +frec.","guid":"LjR8k13KXZtoGFVBQjS1OA","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"• Dilatación VI → ↓FEVI, IC sistólica.","guid":"ZSK_nXjQWZhTpExSqFDPGw","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"3","text":"• Cardiomiopatía\\Nhipertrófica (HCM):","guid":"5FqsBprcDNTn3t6HGuzZ3A","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"• Hipertrofia VI → obstrucción flujo de salida (±), disfunción diastólica.","guid":"nzNvOA1FoSYigmCxZNykDg","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"3","text":"• Cardiomiopatía\\Nrestrictiva (RCM):","guid":"MKUayEqsVFUz2-Gksl4_wA","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"• Rigidez miocárdica → disfunción diastólica sin dilatación.","guid":"ktTDUGRTvQg_itFp3PIOFA","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"3","text":"• Cardiomiopatía arritmogénica del VD\\N(ARVC):","guid":"S8mY1loDgLF0-cQHaQrWrw","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"• Fibro-adiposidad en VD → adelgazamiento miocárdico,\\Ndilatación ventricular, arritmias ventriculares.","guid":"I0ltNDf7sds1Ooj7Nkg3Mg","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"• Sx variables: Arritmias, síncope, IC derecha.","guid":"puorBhc7v1vhgeDTaaMe4g","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"• Tratamiento → individualizado según gravedad.","guid":"ArqoTjHW73bFiOcNIzk48A","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"11","text":"• Evitar ejercicio extenuante.","guid":"f2gP94ZJ_Bx9WR-qZkFWUA","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"3","text":"• Cardiomiopatía inducida\\Npor arritmias (AIC):","guid":"umdvm4raD7pO3FmNnlyF2w","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"• Causa: Arritmias prolongadas (FA, TPSV) → afecta VI.","guid":"LBb9h6ctWie8bqMJYrHj-A","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"• Clínica: Palpitaciones, síncope, signos de arritmia (ECG).","guid":"SDj0TWxCBZSTwlHz1rDIDg","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"• Complicación: IC izquierda en casos graves.","guid":"c8__uyFsyvh-UHCTUv7VcA","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"16","text":"• Tratamiento: Antiarrítmicos (ß-bloqueadores, control rítmico).","guid":"xqIjAriDu27xP1uXsuz_CA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"0","text":"Tipos\\Nprincipales","guid":"iu8BMbQoezDj_F_cPgk2TA","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"• Cardiomiopatía\\Ndilatada (DCM)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"• Etiología:","guid":"3zOulTv-_PvmkIwIONRGSg","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"• Idiopática (+frec)","guid":"RHF-oq9Z5JrB4s4nmgfrdg","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"• Genética (mutación TTN)","guid":"JabbvhDppQsA736NrWLD6g","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"23","text":"• Cardiopatía isquémica","guid":"Ws9Ep9J6EYUwlWk6qb-7gA","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"23","text":"• Infecciosas (virus Coxsackie B, Chagas, VIH)","guid":"87_CGVL-s5TphMS6VzFhrQ","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"23","text":"• Enfermedades sistémicas (sarcoidosis, hemocromatosis, deficiencia de tiamina → beriberi húmeda)","guid":"6hphOI4fb2Q6fXJmm1oz5A","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"23","text":"• Sustancias tóxicas (cocaína, alcohol, fármacos: doxorrubicina)","guid":"_djyXXhze0oMUmof2LL6WQ","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"23","text":"• Cardiomiopatía periparto","guid":"IjmF4XRP7c2o-UvSTVUvjg","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"22","text":"• Fisiopatología:","guid":"Hx65fCrdxSFdVYgdEKfXSQ","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"• Hipertrofia excéntrica VI → ↓ contractilidad ventricular → ↓ FEVI","guid":"Z6VyyIAphZwKARLuk3089g","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"22","text":"• Clínica:","guid":"QX0qmNUCXt-edeAKg3wDcQ","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"• Signos de IC izq y derecha, galope S3, soplo sistólico, arritmias.","guid":"6kAjdp47WyA1R59_Tdqe9w","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"22","text":"• Ecocardiografía:","guid":"wY3vVt2MhZIabB0n82cUcA","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"• Tamaño cavidad VI ↑, FEVI ↓, grosor pared normal o ↓, disfunción sistólica, dilatación biatrial.","guid":"eNdmJgz5FvwG3njSUE14Tg","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"22","text":"• Características\\Nadicionales:","guid":"WRIiEv_kotMK3sirGi_ZGQ","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• +común, mal pronóstico sin trasplante.","guid":"znzl_TdN3z98vDWxdkDQEA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"21","text":"• Cardiomiopatía\\Nhipertrófica (HCM)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"• Etiología:","guid":"UXwONQGMPfJaQjEwFxoPhA","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"• Mutación autosómica dominante (proteína C de unión a miosina,\\Ncadena pesada β-miosina)","guid":"SZojImDTpIABgr1h7AQ_Lw","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"• Idiopática","guid":"jQaNh6aaCgGsB5v08bf9pw","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"39","text":"• Fisiopatología:","guid":"tYIBzOjI77zO2tSDEREj6g","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"• Hipertrofia concéntrica VI (+ tabique interventricular) → ↓ relajación ventricular\\N→ ↓ llenado diastólico → ↓ gasto cardíaco","guid":"Xjznc39Urqa8n6OY7FbanA","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"• Tipo obstructivo (HOCM): obstrucción tracto de salida VI (LVOT)\\N+ regurgitación mitral por SAM (systolic anterior movement)","guid":"m8byos6h07QEma058QxPAw","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"39","text":"• Clínica:","guid":"gFRFn3llv1jCBn_-rcbK0A","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"• Frecuentemente asintomática, disnea, síncope, galope S4, soplo\\Nsistólico holosistólico (regurgitación mitral), muerte súbita.","guid":"cIg0gvSxqPPZs79ew0jfSA","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"39","text":"• Ecocardiografía:","guid":"_bIpEeIEv7nTDvtGmsAEhQ","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"• Tamaño cavidad VI ↓, FEVI normal, grosor pared ↑,\\Nobstrucción LVOT, alteración llenado diastólico.","guid":"VDId-8vCGSeaatGImjFIXw","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"39","text":"• Características\\Nadicionales:","guid":"rimdjjNJuWzPhFgPPc1ItA","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"• Segunda + común, causa principal de\\Nmuerte súbita en atletas/jóvenes.","guid":"ahcaPtogXMh-lehmH13D2Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"21","text":"• Cardiomiopatía restrictiva\\N(RCM)","guid":"f60c27-2HayoYWaBH1zbCA","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"• Etiología:","guid":"GnKUxDUWImRBrxFzSvDt1g","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"• Enfermedades sistémicas (amiloidosis, sarcoidosis, hemocromatosis, esclerosis sistémica)","guid":"9vw4H0bmlolW9mlTZaee8A","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"• Cardiopatías (endocarditis de Löffler, fibroelastosis endocárdica)","guid":"Q2NAxk3Z7XfjC6TJiCn-Uw","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"53","text":"• Fibrosis postradiación","guid":"3shUfKJdd97GomRmSl7eYw","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"52","text":"• Fisiopatología:","guid":"uYLMMUHjBRtXIh4DyZcJjQ","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• Proliferación tejido conectivo → ↓ elasticidad miocárdica\\N→ disfunción diastólica severa, dilatación auricular.","guid":"MGpJAGVg_0zNLKSVJ2ePJQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"52","text":"• Clínica:","guid":"VOtRGyiwe2MGAWF0sKamvA","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"• Signos de IC izq y derecha, disnea, edema.","guid":"wNfJfenh7c8qtyufghWkoQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"52","text":"• Ecocardiografía:","guid":"OFsGHfZDQqBCusNwXdUbKw","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"• Tamaño cavidad VI ↓, FEVI normal o ↑, grosor pared ↑,\\Nllenado diastólico reducido, dilatación auricular.","guid":"hSelBUkdAMWHwk-ymDooDw","children":[]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"52","text":"• Características\\Nadicionales:","guid":"BXZEsaDcPywdCxjh81m98w","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"•  • frecuente en amiloidosis y enfermedades infiltrativas.","guid":"8I5qQwryAYKXj4YHSUjlPQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"0","text":"Diferencias\\Necocardiográficas:","guid":"XdKr1w79p5G9ck94WeYpPw","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"• Tamaño\\Ncavidad VI:","guid":"J7DjkvNMZMHJQZFT3VUB_g","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"• DCM: ↑","guid":"n9MVZlRMYIhMxK_BLzwkkA","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"• HCM: ↓","guid":"HJiUIwDDK9n5tkKOfdpMjg","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"66","text":"• RCM: ↓","guid":"wufkgYe0-5cPgIRVoGiSLg","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"65","text":"• FEVI:","guid":"AooWORCF4430lb8kgclW4w","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"• DCM: ↓","guid":"gBcVzdkfTNL2zUSFTR77gw","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"• HCM: Normal","guid":"q9_ZIzSfsiy9WVVtPg_tbQ","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"• RCM: Normal o ↑","guid":"eT-pUwaEjkMhBN4cJxCtgw","children":[]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"65","text":"• Grosor\\Npared:","guid":"tcKNatli2wYeFobYAKpXTg","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"• DCM: Normal o ↓","guid":"t0-rJuljlkZS87dqvCQOCw","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"74","text":"• HCM: ↑","guid":"qthAy0MOe7vDXUB5POvQJg","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"74","text":"• RCM: ↑","guid":"ItSfUoFRe-bw-pI_M82KxA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"0","text":"Cardiomiopatía arritmogénica del\\Nventrículo derecho (ARVC)","guid":"dnWSS73J9_ZgJynh0jFoMw","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"HaYZlVKb3sqC9c1l3iuGtw","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"•  • común en adultos jóvenes (edad media dx: ∼30\\Naños)","guid":"Lx4XY18-dZuww1uVdIA0ug","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"• Prevalencia: 1:1, 000–2,000 (2,3)","guid":"o1TfGyvtzAfPnBGuPPsD3g","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"78","text":"Etiología","guid":"UCbMzPzGn_O17Ah81fLdDQ","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"• Mutaciones en genes (ej.: JUP)","guid":"SPvohk2-foASFwmyk-eYiQ","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"• Herencia autosómica recesiva o dominante (3,4)","guid":"IIeG4wjLrGk_R6GBoA1EBA","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"78","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"inQNeb5ojJ49i8K-pi51NQ","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"• Muerte celular miocárdica VD → apoptosis, inflamación, reemplazo por tejido fibroadiposo\\N→ adelgazamiento pared VD → dilatación → arritmia y disfunción ventricular (2)","guid":"7GlwMaqg60h7DtgN43ECag","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"• VI puede verse afectado, pero consecuencias menos graves.","guid":"FWcbTIr88ecJ0NxmRBAz-A","children":[]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"78","text":"Clínica","guid":"zaH7gmA_QKPedPrWnf3WxQ","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"• Variable, muchos pacientes asintomáticos.","guid":"L_cDMJfBpnV1Vkzz9ntONA","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"88","text":"• Angina, disnea, edema periférico, ascitis, congestión hepática/esplénica.","guid":"o1yXuK-AeFLn6qQUwi_azQ","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"88","text":"• Palpitaciones, síncope, muerte súbita\\N(sobre todo durante/después de ejercicio).","guid":"27wd_vJKbSDLBwym5s0v3Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"78","text":"Diagnóstico\\N(3,2,5)","guid":"e3WuupzMNCDFzL51CEMoZw","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"• Criterios\\NAHA:","guid":"WtuqsF1-Yib94AYiGghz0A","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"1. Disfunción/anomalías estructurales VD (eco, RMN, angiografía VD)","guid":"q2Q83fhmK2_quI8CKLlBrA","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"2. Características histológicas (biopsia miocárdica)","guid":"r0d5sjykreGWyQelO_qt9g","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"93","text":"3. Anomalías repolarización (ECG)","guid":"yFb0xylIZeQaX2pD-o9JQQ","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"93","text":"4. Anomalías despolarización/conducción (ECG)","guid":"j9HhTi2XfIBpvJMPwUsAsA","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"93","text":"5. Arritmias (ECG)","guid":"KC2hgCKrBwE4968S4FBCww","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"93","text":"6. Antecedentes familiares (confirmación ARVC por criterios, cirugía, autopsia, prueba genética).","guid":"W3VkurujPXjVFZRwdW9UHw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"78","text":"Hallazgos","guid":"op8XfRmpu0FEaKHdn0fzmw","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"• ECG:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"• Alteraciones repolarización en derivaciones\\Nprecordiales derechas (V1-3).","guid":"CyNj2rtL0B9r326FpAYpVg","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"• Posible onda epsilon (al final del complejo QRS ancho)\\N→ específico ARVC pero solo en ∼⅓ pacientes.","guid":"Hl9Ywo3UP27X3AbZs6OT7Q","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"• Duración QRS ↑, taquicardia\\Nventricular, extrasístoles ventriculares.","guid":"POxo_yORUS3joMnwq-nfxw","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"100","text":"• Ecocardiografía/RMN\\Ncardíaca:","guid":"VcGDx741PLEMOZwRSC8TFA","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"• Agrandamiento VD, anomalías movimiento pared,\\N↓FEVD, aneurismas localizados VD.","guid":"5a9z6w0DZmeaZTkPheeMqw","children":[]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"100","text":"• Biopsia endomiocárdica: Reemplazo fibroadiposo tejido miocárdico.","guid":"MB8c7diZpSWBVoiOxFgaDw","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"100","text":"• Genética: Mutaciones en plakoglobina (JUP), desmoplaquina (DSP),\\Nplakofilina-2 (PKP2), desmogleína-2 (DSG2), desmocolina (DSC2) (4).","guid":"iyg1IlIRWjXVv5vQsr-3Uw","children":[]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"78","text":"Manejo (5,6)","guid":"Gjqhr7OYRAiiMPXI7EJcow","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"• Evitar ejercicio intenso.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"• Antiarrítmicos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"• Farmacológico: ß-bloqueadores (ej.: sotalol),\\Namiodarona, calcioantagonistas.","guid":"UkeqGrhljNUm1RS3Ok5d2g","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"109","text":"• Invasivo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"• Implantación DAI en pacientes alto riesgo (ej.: afectación VI).","guid":"Tr7ceeCKNzBMwodCKTMUtw","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"• Ablación por radiofrecuencia (solo tratamiento adyuvante).","guid":"SpXOKhFuxZTDqWiBM38bsg","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"113","text":"• Trasplante cardíaco en casos refractarios.","guid":"CK8sPar9oc-R1qyXbnD_bw","children":[]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"109","text":"• Tamizaje y consejo genético a familiares de 1er grado.","guid":"xSpTAGx3q-m-fl3Pka77ww","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"0","text":"Cardiomiopatías\\Nno clasificadas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"1. No compactación ventricular\\Nizquierda (LVNC) (7)","guid":"1wxEDbT-tlWCwjIbn7Xgrg","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"• Definición: Cardiomiopatía hereditaria rara, asociada con anormalidades estructurales del miocardio VI\\N(trabeculaciones prominentes y recesos intertrabeculares profundos).","guid":"7RiXzCpMGbGtKm12qhTFNg","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":"• Clínica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"• Signos de IC y arritmias (disnea, edema, dolor torácico, palpitaciones, síncope).","guid":"WGONJCNr34S6sVPXGn_JnQ","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"• Tromboembolismos.","guid":"K3TKPJ_7y7jlMjoJ9HfsdA","children":[]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"119","text":"• Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"• Ecocardiografía/RMN cardíaca → Engrosamiento pared VI, malla\\Ntrabecular prominente, flujo anormal en recesos profundos.","guid":"MP7DsvVQ-9SyWz8Ce31Ckw","children":[]}]},{"id":"126","parent":"119","text":"• Tratamiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"• Sin tratamiento causal disponible.","guid":"e1jPE5jLX8kr1er9oF7Gag","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"• Evitar ejercicio intenso.","guid":"epeuY4G-Jq8PSWYB32axgg","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"119","text":"• Tratamiento sintomático\\Nde complicaciones (IC).","guid":"hoTvf-Eo2-AW3RBA7Ea1Cg","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"• Prevención tromboembolismo.","guid":"96xBw8flOWlCU5OfPcFlFg","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"• DAI, trasplante cardíaco.","guid":"te90AfOgSe_9ZjcAFbBFUw","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"129","text":"• Consejería familiar/genética.","guid":"kd7cp992V4GNoy2RyFoANw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"118","text":"2. Cardiomiopatía inducida\\Npor arritmias (AIC) (8,9)","guid":"QiApperzdW4hZznRNlvS0w","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"• Definición: Arritmias auriculares o ventriculares recurrentes o persistentes →\\Ncambios estructurales cardíacos + disfunción VI (potencialmente reversible).","guid":"7fGO0r7C3Ew8s_k9997KYw","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"• Etiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"• Taquiarritmias supraventriculares (taquicardia, FA, flutter auricular, taquicardia reentrante supraventricular).","guid":"WKisWygAcg2-2sDWy0IJWA","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"• Taquiarritmia ventricular (menos frecuente).","guid":"9qG-WCv1mOLY5bjHbcEvOA","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"135","text":"• Ectopia auricular/ventricular (con o sin taquicardia).","guid":"AP5xsJvJo5IFs0VO4-dxSw","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"133","text":"• Clínica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"• Signos de arritmia subyacente (palpitaciones, síncope).","guid":"nQASosVjWEpM9NkyZ3DiGA","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"• Signos de IC izquierda (disnea, dolor torácico, edema pulmonar).","guid":"qfNvEIN5aBXEo1RCwr-Zrw","children":[]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"133","text":"• Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"• ECG → taquiarritmia, focos ectópicos.","guid":"AOEIfjQWpDYiFPhMQl-q9Q","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"• Monitoreo cardíaco (Holter).","guid":"mnzv4tbC3uHUi-KZ5AVpyQ","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"142","text":"• Ecocardiografía/RMN → evaluar estructura/función cardíaca (medición FEVI).","guid":"TbTy9sSu6ItDsTrL4JvuDA","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"142","text":"• Excluir otras causas (angiografía coronaria para descartar cardiopatía isquémica).","guid":"GGUcV1YjgP0orK_aPMq1bw","children":[]}]},{"id":"147","parent":"133","text":"• Tratamiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"• ß-bloqueadores → manejo IC, control de frecuencia en taquiarritmias.","guid":"2wNejyrlr9Oc0Tm6xgpk6A","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"147","text":"• Antiarrítmicos (amiodarona) → control de ritmo en taquiarritmias.","guid":"txDcLswrAk8leuyHUYQLDQ","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"147","text":"• Ablación por catéter → control de ritmo, focos ectópicos.","guid":"xsi6skvEWwAs6ItHT1jwbg","children":[]}]}]}]}]},"node_count":150,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Cardiología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Cardiología","filename":"Cardiomiopatias-2024-1","id":"map_268","resolved_references":[]}